        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "DNA was extracted from bacterial isolates using the DNeasy® Blood and Tissue kit (Qiagen, Venlo, Netherlands) and from fungal isolates using the DNeasy® PowerSoil® kit (Qiagen,",
